This paper deals with the problem of compressing deep neural networks, which is a topic that spans multiple sub-fields of computer science. However, given that the paper focuses on the optimization of the compression process and the use of quantization, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CV (Computer Vision). Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these fields are also relevant to the topic of neural network compression.
